|{{flag|Michigan}}&lt;ref&gt;[https://www.michigan.gov/taxes/0,4676,7-238-75545_43715-153723--,00.html What are the current tax rate and exemption amounts?], Michigan Department of Treasury.&lt;/ref&gt;{{efn|name=most}} || 4.25% || [[List of municipalities in Michigan|some municipalities]]&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.michigan.gov/taxes/0,4676,7-238-75545_43715-153955--,00.html What cities impose an income tax?], Michigan Department of Treasury.&lt;/ref&gt; || 1 to 2.4%
